| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1325 — Recovery Inhibition (8base)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c3ae3b98-1eef-52d6-a6fb-d0d5cc5ecb48"
